title: Bug 109350: Output parameter should display in data set dialog.
description: The output parameter is not displayed in the data set dialog.
OB: Currently, when calling the stored procedure from the Oracle database, the query result is stored in the output parameter as an object. However, the output parameter is not being displayed in the data set dialog.
EB: The output parameter should be visible in the data set dialog.
SR:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Call the stored procedure from the Oracle database.
2. Check the data set dialog to verify if the output parameter is displayed.
